sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Lambda
    participant S3
    participant Instagram as Instagram CDN
    participant Gemini as Google Gemini

    Client->>Lambda: GET ?url=
    Lambda->>S3: Fetch session (if not cached)
    S3-->>Lambda: Session file
    Lambda->>Instagram: Scrape post (Instaloader)
    Instagram-->>Lambda: imageUrl + caption
    Lambda->>Instagram: Fetch image bytes
    Instagram-->>Lambda: image bytes
    Lambda->>Gemini: imageBase64 + caption
    Gemini-->>Lambda: EventData JSON
    Lambda-->>Client: EventData JSON + _timing
